<~> Welcome!
<~> 
<~> So, you want to know a little bit about us? Well here's the skinny:
<~> 
<~> Armor:   Primarily Cloth. Some leather pieces are allowed in specific
<~>          equipment slots.
<~> Weapons: Medium swords, daggers, staves, small magical shields.
<~> Magic:   Mix of self and opponent status-effecting magic, damaging 
<~>          magic, and generic support magic. 
<~> Align:   The lunar entities Dailos, Markas, and Tekal will not aid
<~>          those who are too far towards demonic alignment.
<~> 
<~> Also be forewarned that the life of a Lunar is not easy. The price
<~> we pay for receiving the aid of the great Lunar entities and not
<~> having to use those silly hand-motions and annoying voice commands
<~> to use our magic does result in our spells backfiring sometimes. You
<~> get used to it and it almost never results in your own death. Well,
<~> make sure you read the "almost" part of that last sentence. It's
<~> not all bad though! The power of the moons is immeasurable, and the
<~> fact that they provide you with the ability to summon even a small
<~> amount of it, is well worth the chance of failure.
<~>
<~> The Lunar guild hall can be found west of DarkWind City
<~> up on a mountain top: 4:w,6:n,climb,up,east,enter
<~> ====================================================================

